title: Who are you?
body:
{{champion:238}} Poor Zed. You have lost the way. You cannot **_see_** the light. You have been enveloped in darkness. 
---
{{champion:37}} Sona. What a shame, that you are **_mute_**. You cannot talk, and those around you cannot hear.
---
{{champion:86}} Garen, I know what bothers you. I know what you want in your **_heart_**, but you cannot have her. You can't be with the one you love.
---
{{champion:254}} Vi, you troubled soul. You are torn, but you know that you have to do what you **_feel_** is right. You can't let the innocent get hurt.
---
---
I know who you are, I know your _weakness_.
---
-DeadEye (Jhin)

replies.body:
{{champion:83}}  Yorick, an unheard of champion in the League of Legends. What a sad life it is to not be able to_ walk_ into a bar with counters.

I don't know who you are, you don't have a weakness.

-Deadeye (Jhin)
Where did you get this "quote" from?
Shhhh... It's a secret to everybody...
